{"tid":1729753,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【被割席】高志森棄用《南海》台前幕後 叫香港演藝人不要自視過高","createTime":"2019-11-17T10:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:03:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":131,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"e6246ff572a981697bf97dff3d61e233622aee5b","tid":1729753,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"網傳高志森被《南海十三郎》舞台劇的台前幕後割席，明年4月的演出取消！《蘋果》聯絡高志森求證，但沒有回覆。雖然高志森對《蘋果》不理不睬，但原來就有在「南海2016巡迴演員」的WhatsApp群組中作出回應，以短訊承認明年西九不演了，更大口氣地表示可以不要香港團隊，巡演全國。<br />\n<br />\n高志森在群組中留言：「大家別亂傳了。暴徒亂港，治安不好，明年西九就不演了。所謂的『杯葛者』也就不用圍爐取暖了。我團絕對可以演一個沒有任何香港台前幕後參與南海十三郎，巡演全國！天大地大，中國市場很大！香港演藝人也就不要自視過高了！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191117/large/1573983741_d55d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191117%2Flarge%2F1573983741_d55d.jpg&h=a31a078d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191117/60278249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191117%2F60278249&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=49f3b164\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191117%2F60278249&h=2cfc2b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191117/60278249</a>"},{"pid":"cc0834e9fbc40bcddf3f6a01a6fbb0b79feda1d2","tid":1729753,"uid":50801,"like":142,"dislike":0,"score":142,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"一條友杯葛全個劇團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec4a8c3d88f37cca4506e0f697a59176bda57bc","tid":1729753,"uid":165361,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:54:34.000Z","msg":"香港演藝人也就不要自視過高了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi