三郎》舞台劇的台前幕後割席，明年4月的演出取消！《蘋果》聯絡高志森求證，但沒有回覆。雖然高志森對《蘋果》不理不睬，但原來就有在「南海2016巡迴演員」的WhatsApp群組中作出回應，以短訊承認明年西九不演了，更大口氣地表示可以不要香港團隊，巡演全國。<br />\n<br />\n高志森在群組中留言：「大家別亂傳了。暴徒亂港，治安不好，明年西九就不演了。所謂的『杯葛者』也就不用圍爐取暖了。我團絕對可以演一個沒有任何香港台前幕後參與南海十三郎，巡演全國！天大地大，中國市場很大！香港演藝人也就不要自視過高了！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191117/large/1573983741_d55d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191117%2Flarge%2F1573983741_d55d.jpg&h=a31a078d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191117/60278249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191117%2F60278249&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=49f3b164\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191117%2F60278249&h=2cfc2b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191117/60278249</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R9VWjkv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR9VWjkv.gif&h=8aeaf9fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c0c0687b3711d1d0061f4a703cca877df5b65a8","tid":1729753,"uid":271081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6246ff572a981697bf97dff3d61e233622aee5b","tid":1729753,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"網傳高志森被《南海十三郎》舞台劇的台前幕後割席，明年4月的演出取消！《蘋果》聯絡高志森求證，但沒有回覆。雖然高志森對《蘋果》不理不睬，但原來就有在「南海2016巡迴演員」的WhatsApp群組中作出回應，以短訊承認明年西九不演了，更大口氣地表示可以不要香港團隊，巡演全國。<br />\n<br />\n高志森在群組中留言：「大家別亂傳了。暴徒亂港，治安不好，明年西九就不演了。所謂的『杯葛者』也就不用圍爐取暖了。我團絕對可以演一個沒有任何香港台前幕後參與南海十三郎，巡演全國！天大地大，中國市場很大！香港演藝人也就不要自視過高了！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191117/large/1573983741_d55d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191117%2Flarge%2F1573983741_d55d.jpg&h=a31a078d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191117/60278249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191117%2F60278249&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=49f3b164\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191117%2F60278249&h=2cfc2b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191117/60278249</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:54:30.000Z","msg":"條低b森番大陸啦，留香港托咩，有人睇佢啲劇？"},{"pid":"5277ecc4e004c10e71376c78d5d7da4b080301df","tid":1729753,"uid":246962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"謝君豪雖然好正，但佢其實都係食老本，佢而家少做話劇，但每隔幾年就翻做13郎，好悶囉，做下多些新嘢好嗎"},{"pid":"180c11755e3df4aeb5a36796bbe84e72eac6f1df","tid":1729753,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5277ecc4e004c10e71376c78d5d7da4b080301df","tid":1729753,"uid":246962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"謝君豪雖然好正，但佢其實都係食老本，佢而家少做話劇，但每隔幾年就翻做13郎，好悶囉，做下多些新嘢好嗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"佢唔係有拍大陸劇咩?"},{"pid":"a42a901bd04541a0b134ca525c7afdef84425168","tid":1729753,"uid":246962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"180c11755e3df4aeb5a36796bbe84e72eac6f1df","tid":1729753,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5277ecc4e004c10e71376c78d5d7da4b080301df","tid":1729753,"uid":246962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"謝君豪雖然好正，但佢其實都係食老本，佢而家少做話劇，但每隔幾年就翻做13郎，好悶囉，做下多些新嘢好嗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"佢唔係有拍大陸劇咩?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:16:22.000Z"